== Black holes == In January 2014, [[Chandra X-ray Observatory|Chandra X-Ray Observatory]] claimed to have made discovery of a new [[List of black holes|supermassive black hole candidate]] disrupting star in the Abell 1795.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://chandra.harvard.edu/press/14_releases/press_010814.html|title=Chandra Press Room :: Death By Black Hole In Small Galaxy? :: 08 January 14|website=chandra.harvard.edu|language=en|access-date=2018-07-18}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/chandra/multimedia/white-dwarf-system-abell-1795.html|title=Dwarf Galaxy, Galaxy Cluster Abell 1795|last=Boen|first=Brooke|date=2015-05-06|work=NASA|access-date=2018-07-18|language=en}}</ref>
