'''''Grape vine virus A''''' (GVA) is a plant virus and the type species in the genus ''[[Vitivirus]]''.<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Goszczynski DE, du Preez J, Burger JT |title=Molecular divergence of Grapevine virus A (GVA) variants associated with Shiraz disease in South Africa |journal=Virus Res. |volume=138 |issue=1-2 |pages=105–10 |year=2008 |pmid=18822325 |doi=10.1016/j.virusres.2008.08.014 |url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0168-1702(08)00321-3}}</ref>

