{{virus-stub}}

{{Italic title}} {{Virusbox | name = ''Negarnaviricota'' | image = File:Negarnaviricota montage.jpg | image_alt = 300px | image_caption = A montage of [[transmission electron micrograph]]s of some viruses in the phylum ''Negarnaviricota''. Not to scale. Species from left to right, top to bottom: ''[[Zaire ebolavirus]]'', ''[[Sin Nombre virus|Sin Nombre orthohantavirus]]'', ''[[Human respiratory syncytial virus|Human orthopneumovirus]]'', ''[[Henipavirus#Hendra virus|Hendra henipavirus]]'', an unidentified [[rhabdovirus]], ''[[Measles virus|Measles morbillivirus]]''. | status = | status_system = | status_ref = | taxon = Negarnaviricota | authority = | synonyms = | synonyms_ref = | subdivision_ranks = Subphyla | subdivision = *''[[Haploviricotina]]'' <small></small> *''[[Polyploviricotina]]'' <small></small> }}
The [[phylum]] '''''Negarnaviricota''''' includes all [[negative-sense single-stranded RNA virus]]es (group V in [[Baltimore classification]]) except ''[[Hepatitis D|Hepatitis delta virus]]''. It is divided into the subphyla ''[[Haploviricotina]]'' and ''[[Polyploviricotina]]''.<ref name="ICTV">{{Cite web|url=https://talk.ictvonline.org/files/master-species-lists/m/msl/7992|title=ICTV Master Species List 2018a v1|last=|first=|date=|website=International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=4 November 2018}}</ref> {{As of|2018|November|4}} it is the sole viral phylum to be established, though it does not include all viruses as many have not been assigned to a phylum.<ref name="ICTV"/>
==Taxonomy== The taxonomy of the ''Negarnaviricota'' down to the rank of [[Order (biology)|order]] is as follows:<ref name="ICTV"/>
* Subphylum ''Haploviricotina'' ** Class ''[[Chunqiuviricetes]]'' *** Order ''[[Muvirales]]'' ** Class ''[[Milneviricetes]]'' *** Order ''[[Serpentovirales]]'' ** Class ''[[Monjiviricetes]]'' *** Order ''[[Jingchuvirales]]'' *** Order ''[[Mononegavirales]]'' ** Class ''[[Yunchangviricetes]]'' *** Order ''[[Goujianvirales]]'' * Subphylum ''Polyploviricotina'' ** Class ''[[Ellioviricetes]]'' *** Order ''[[Bunyavirales]]'' ** Class ''[[Insthoviricetes]]'' *** Order ''[[Articulavirales]]''
==References== {{Reflist}}
